    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551630/extras/f3ce945502e08b0a2b3dd679b0b773be.avif?t=1749385651\" width=616 height=72 /></span>平静的村庄如今正遭受缝魔的威胁，她们的缝会让看到的男性成为废人。名叫嘉尔的女生决定踏上寻找据说可以对抗缝魔的存在，“传说中的封魔”的旅途。实际上，这个传说中的封魔是一个名为辰巳的疯魔黑道，他是从另一个世界穿越来此的。两人决定一起解决缝魔肆虐的秘密，并终结她们对世界的威胁！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551630/extras/72d84896fa30519ef1f78d05744b1ba9.avif?t=1749385651\" width=616 height=72 /></span>在经典的回合制战斗中解决危险的魔物！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >白天和夜晚可以探索村子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >捕捉缝魔并让她们和自己并肩战斗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551630/extras/38f1cf14092d9b2d1a981131b3672968.avif?t=1749385651\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551630/extras/fce5eebe002b3c3a45f92f8fc787814c.avif?t=1749385651\" width=616 height=274 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551630/extras/8d448e1ff92342ec47ed50e5b82fd173.avif?t=1749385651\" width=616 height=274 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551630/extras/c8737118caa0f1c2a92ff558c5494d3e.avif?t=1749385651\" width=616 height=72 /></span><strong>白天和夜晚探索村庄</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >白天可以接受村民委托，帮他们解决各种困难。晚上则能看到村民们不为人知的一面，并借此深入了解嘉尔的性格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>俘获她们!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以捕捉缝魔的首领们，一旦满足了某些条件，她们就会和你并肩作战！</p>",
